subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
It is with great regret to inform you that your  outstanding Cashier
Check has returned undelivered due to incomplete or incorrect
recipient address. We are sorry you did not receive your parcel as
promptly as you expected.
Please write down your real and correct name and shipping address,
including your mobile phone number, carefully and completely.
With kindest regards,
Dr. Souley Amadou
drsouleyamadou15@gmail.com
General Counsel and Director of the Legal Service Department,

subject: Re:   Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Dr. Souley Adou,

I appreciate your prompt response and concern regarding the issue with my Cashier Check. It's quite unfortunate that there was a mix-up with the recipient address.

However, I'm a bit confused about how this could have happened as I usually double-check all my details before sending them out. Could you please provide more information on what exactly was incorrect or incomplete? This would help me avoid such mistakes in the future.

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Kimberly
